name: DailyDrawingInspiration
0:
”Alexa, what's my Flash Briefing?”
”Alexa, play my Flash Briefing”
skdetail:
Flash Briefing Skill
This skill contains: dynamic content.
des:
Want something new to draw everyday? Just add this flash briefing to your arsenal, and you'll get a new prompt each morning! (or, whenever you ask Alexa for your flash briefing)

Want to hear the daily prompt again, or just get a new one? Check out the Drawing Inspiration skill (http://bit.ly/Drawspiration_AlexaSkill).
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
